PROJECT TITLE: Predicting High Risk Substance Use Among Women of Childbearing Age Using Machine Learning: Insights from the 2023 TEDS-D Dataset. 

DATASET: Treatment Episode Data Set - Discharges 2023 (TEDS-D 2023). 

This project was performed as part of George Mason University's HI 780: Data Mining in Health Care course taught by Dr. Abdul Hafeez in the spring 2026 semester.

